      "date": "2014-06-12 17:59:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\nIn fact if we look at all usage of handle_recovery_req, we can see the return value of it is never checked.\nAlso with this code the return is always 0 which makes no sense.\n\nI suspect we should just convert it to a void function instead and get rid of rc altogether",
